                <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Valerius <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>ani</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>epos</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Messal</abbr><ex>la</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Serveilius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Isauricus ce<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ores</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>ex <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>enatus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>onsulto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>termin</abbr><ex>averunt</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Serveilius <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/>Isauricus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Valerius <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>ani</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>epos</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Messall</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>cens</abbr><ex>ores</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>ex <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>enatus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>onsulto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>termi</abbr><ex>naverunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Stein gehört zu einer Serie von 20 beinahe gleichen Grenzsteinen, die am Tiber zwischen Ponte Milvio und San Paolo fuori le mura gefunden wurden; sie stammen von der Tiberbegrenzung des Jahres 55 v. Chr. nach Überschwemmung. Dieser Stein ist auf Vorder- und Rückseite beschrieben. Gesamthöhe: etwa 223,4. (B): AE 1984: Rückseite Z. 4/5/6: keine Angaben der Zeilenfälle.</p>
            </div>
